### Test Chat & Conversation API

# Notes:
- Replace `REPLACE_TOKEN` with a valid JWT returned from `/users/login` or paste your token directly.
- Replace `REPLACE_CONVERSATION_ID` and `REPLACE_MESSAGE_ID` with IDs returned by the create calls below.

### Login (get token)
POST http://localhost:3000/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get User Info (verify token)
GET http://localhost:3000/users/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5ZDNjODM5MWI5ODIxYTM1MTM5YmY2NiIsImlhdCI6MTc3NTk3ODcwNiwiZXhwIjoxNzc2MDAzOTA2fQ.Fkvxlq4YlvAnMAd-syge1x469s7H4DT-zZz6JNtmlb4

### Create Conversation (project)
POST http://localhost:3000/conversations
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5ZDNjODM5MWI5ODIxYTM1MTM5YmY2NiIsImlhdCI6MTc3NTk3ODcwNiwiZXhwIjoxNzc2MDAzOTA2fQ.Fkvxlq4YlvAnMAd-syge1x469s7H4DT-zZz6JNtmlb4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "project": "69d3c8391b9821a35139bf6c",
  "name": "Project Discussion",
  "type": "project",
  "participants": ["69d3c8391b9821a35139bf67", "69d3c8391b9821a35139bf68"],
  "metadata": {}
}

### Get Conversations (list)
GET http://localhost:3000/conversations
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5ZDNjODM5MWI5ODIxYTM1MTM5YmY2NiIsImlhdCI6MTc3NTk3ODcwNiwiZXhwIjoxNzc2MDAzOTA2fQ.Fkvxlq4YlvAnMAd-syge1x469s7H4DT-zZz6JNtmlb4

### Get Conversation Details
GET http://localhost:3000/conversations/69db496615ee04cbfbccf556
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5ZDNjODM5MWI5ODIxYTM1MTM5YmY2NiIsImlhdCI6MTc3NTk3ODcwNiwiZXhwIjoxNzc2MDAzOTA2fQ.Fkvxlq4YlvAnMAd-syge1x469s7H4DT-zZz6JNtmlb4

### Add Participant
POST http://localhost:3000/conversations/69db496615ee04cbfbccf556/participants
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5ZDNjODM5MWI5ODIxYTM1MTM5YmY2NiIsImlhdCI6MTc3NTk3ODcwNiwiZXhwIjoxNzc2MDAzOTA2fQ.Fkvxlq4YlvAnMAd-syge1x469s7H4DT-zZz6JNtmlb4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "69d3c8391b9821a35139bf66"
}

### Update Conversation
PUT http://localhost:3000/conversations/69db496615ee04cbfbccf556
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5ZDNjODM5MWI5ODIxYTM1MTM5YmY2NiIsImlhdCI6MTc3NTk3ODcwNiwiZXhwIjoxNzc2MDAzOTA2fQ.Fkvxlq4YlvAnMAd-syge1x469s7H4DT-zZz6JNtmlb4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Conversation Name",
  "metadata": { "description": "Updated via test file" }
}

### Remove Participant (by URL)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/conversations/69db496615ee04cbfbccf556/participants/69d3c8391b9821a35139bf68
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5ZDNjODM5MWI5ODIxYTM1MTM5YmY2NiIsImlhdCI6MTc3NTk3ODcwNiwiZXhwIjoxNzc2MDAzOTA2fQ.Fkvxlq4YlvAnMAd-syge1x469s7H4DT-zZz6JNtmlb4

### --- Chat message tests ---

### Send Text Message
POST http://localhost:3000/chats/conversation/69db496615ee04cbfbccf556
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5ZDNjODM5MWI5ODIxYTM1MTM5YmY2NiIsImlhdCI6MTc3NTk3ODcwNiwiZXhwIjoxNzc2MDAzOTA2fQ.Fkvxlq4YlvAnMAd-syge1x469s7H4DT-zZz6JNtmlb4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "text",
  "content": "Hello from test client"
}

### Send Image/File Message (with attachments)
POST http://localhost:3000/chats/conversation/69db496615ee04cbfbccf556
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5ZDNjODM5MWI5ODIxYTM1MTM5YmY2NiIsImlhdCI6MTc3NTk3ODcwNiwiZXhwIjoxNzc2MDAzOTA2fQ.Fkvxlq4YlvAnMAd-syge1x469s7H4DT-zZz6JNtmlb4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "image",
  "content": "Image uploaded",
  "attachments": [
    { "url": "http://localhost:3000/uploads/sample.jpg", "filename": "sample.jpg", "mimeType": "image/jpeg", "size": 12345 }
  ]
}

### List Messages (latest first, optional: ?limit=50&before=ISODate)
GET http://localhost:3000/chats/conversation/69db496615ee04cbfbccf556?limit=50
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5ZDNjODM5MWI5ODIxYTM1MTM5YmY2NiIsImlhdCI6MTc3NTk3ODcwNiwiZXhwIjoxNzc2MDAzOTA2fQ.Fkvxlq4YlvAnMAd-syge1x469s7H4DT-zZz6JNtmlb4

### Edit Message (replace REPLACE_MESSAGE_ID with id returned from create)
PUT http://localhost:3000/chats/69db4afe3324c55bc6f1b2f0
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5ZDNjODM5MWI5ODIxYTM1MTM5YmY2NiIsImlhdCI6MTc3NTk3ODcwNiwiZXhwIjoxNzc2MDAzOTA2fQ.Fkvxlq4YlvAnMAd-syge1x469s7H4DT-zZz6JNtmlb4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Edited message content"
}

### Delete Message (soft delete)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/chats/69db4afe3324c55bc6f1b2f0
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5ZDNjODM5MWI5ODIxYTM1MTM5YmY2NiIsImlhdCI6MTc3NTk3ODcwNiwiZXhwIjoxNzc2MDAzOTA2fQ.Fkvxlq4YlvAnMAd-syge1x469s7H4DT-zZz6JNtmlb4

### Helpful workflow notes
- Run `Login` first and copy the token into `REPLACE_TOKEN`.
- After creating a conversation, copy its `_id` into `69db496615ee04cbfbccf556`.
- After sending a message, copy its `_id` into `REPLACE_MESSAGE_ID` to test edit/delete.



